      <div class="col-md-8 col-sm-12">
        <h1>Decreasing Numbers</h1>
        The Monarch's dwindling population is especially apparent when they all gather together at their hibernation sites.
        Below, a chart shows the decrease in the amount of space these colonies occupy during the winter.
    </div>

